meta {
  name: Generate - Hello HF (smoke test)
  type: http
  seq: 19
}

post {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reel/generate
  body: json
  auth: bearer
}

auth:bearer {
  token: {{apiKey}}
}

body:json {
  {
    "mode": "hello-hf",
    "endCard": { "platform": "universal" }
  }
}

docs {
  Smoke test — exercises the full HF rendering pipeline (compose → render
  → upload) without any LLM/TTS/screenshot. Renders in ~10 s. Useful to:

    - verify worker is up after a deploy
    - confirm MinIO/R2 storage round-trip works
    - check end-card system end-to-end (default `wave-text` for hello-hf)
    - smoke-test changes to the HF runtime

  Cheapest mode in the system. Free.
}
